      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CLASSIC BOODIE (1) has a strong overall record having five wins and 11 places from 24 starts but was out of the money last time when fifth (19.98) over 352m at this track. Solid record here winning four races. Drawn the fence and expected to go close. EQUITY (2) is better than last start when fourth (20.13) in a Grade 5 at Capalaba over 366m. Strike rate this course strong having won two of four tries. The form out of last race has been strong. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. ASKERN VIOLET (6) is in top form, scoring by 2.25 lengths (25.29) over 457m at this track and making it back to back wins. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. In great recent form and expected to measure up again. FEDERAL SAKI (4) was in the money last start here at this trip - likely to feature again.",
